# 🧑‍💼 User Management System

A full-stack **User Management System** built with **Next.js 15 (App Router)** for the frontend and **Express.js + Prisma + PostgreSQL** for the backend.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Add, view, and delete users
- 🔍 Real-time search by **User ID**
- 🖼 Avatar picker with dynamic previews using **DiceBear API**
- 💡 Responsive UI with **Framer Motion** animations
- 🎯 Fully validated forms using **Zod + TypeScript**
- 🧩 Modular component structure with **Shadcn UI**
- 📅 Stores and displays **user creation date**

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Frontend        | Backend      | Database   | Others                    |
|----------------|--------------|------------|---------------------------|
| Next.js 15      | Express.js   | PostgreSQL | Prisma ORM                |
| TypeScript      | Node.js      |            | Zod Validation            |
| Shadcn UI       | REST API     |            | Framer Motion Animations  |

---

## 📂 Project Structure
digitalH/
├── frontend/ # Next.js (App Router) 
│ └── src/ 
│ └── app/ 
│ ├── users/ # User list page 
│ ├── add-user/ # Add user page 
│ └── layouts/ # Shared layout
├── backend/ # Express.js + Prisma 
│ ├── controllers/ 
│ ├── routes/ 
│ └── validations/ 
└── prisma/ # Prisma schema & migrations


---

## 🧪 How to Run Locally

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/afnan41/digitalH.git
cd digitalH


cd backend
npm install
npx prisma migrate dev
npm run dev


cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev

/*The app will be running on: http://localhost:3000*/



💡 Notes
Fully responsive layout across all devices.

Smooth and engaging UI powered by animations.

Modular and maintainable codebase.

RESTful backend built to scale.


